Module org.apache.logging.log4j
Package org.apache.logging.log4j.message

Interface MessageFactory

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    MessageFactory2
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractMessageFactory, FormattedMessageFactory, LocalizedMessageFactory, MessageFormatMessageFactory, ParameterizedMessageFactory, ParameterizedNoReferenceMessageFactory, ReusableMessageFactory, SimpleMessageFactory, StringFormatterMessageFactory
    public interface MessageFactory
    Creates messages. Implementations can provide different message format syntaxes.
    See Also:
    ParameterizedMessageFactory, StringFormatterMessageFactory
